data.description: Don't miss this updated 4 bed 2 bath 1 car garage with extended 2-3 car concrete parking area including storage shed! It has such a park feel with fully landscaped backyard that is fully fenced in with extended concrete patio areas out back. Plenty of space to entertain. This home has been fully renovated with exterior Stucco, Interior has all new carpet, and Wood floors throughout main, laminant flooring in the basement with new carpet in the lower level bedrooms. Also don't forget to look at this beautiful cooks kitchen stainless steel appliances, updated cabinetry, extended height with plenty of storage. The Bathrooms on both levels have been remodeled with new vanity, ceramic tile, decorative mosaic tiles and glass shower surround in the basement All newer lighting and faucets throughout in Antique bronze gives elegant accents to all of the updates. There is also a fireplace to keep you warm on the Cool Colorado nights. Come see this home before it's gone!
